Rating: 4
For all who commented on the prep time, I have the perfect solution. Follow the recipe as written, and instead of simmering 2 hours, pressure cook for 10 minutes, then reduce sauce slightly 5-10 minutes before mixing with the pasta. Total cook to serve time was about 1 hour 30 minutes. I was skeptical, but it was absolutely delicious. I can't image it tasting better the conventional way. Try it!

